videos.headline: Saban says Bama used underdog mentality as fuel vs. UGA
videos.description: In a humor-filled conversation, Alabama's Nick Saban explains how the Tide utilized the media's underdog storylines against Georgia.

videos.headline: Saban thanks media for 'yummy' rat poison
videos.description: Nick Saban praises the media for putting out positive rat poison for the Crimson Tide.
